{"tid":501737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕大餐] 孝女「食母親骨灰」念亡母　","createTime":"2017-12-17T07:03:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T17:28:48.000Z","uid":72478,"like":4,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bee25f87431ed658103c6ffa80f275812afd084b","tid":501737,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T07:03:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2-prod.mirror.co.uk/incoming/article11702547.ece/ALTERNATES/s810/SUNDAYPEOPLE-PROD-Ashesed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2-prod.mirror.co.uk%2Fincoming%2Farticle11702547.ece%2FALTERNATES%2Fs810%2FSUNDAYPEOPLE-PROD-Ashesed.jpg&h=f4e08377&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一名女子今年5月喪母，為了懷念亡母，她決定在聖誕佳節，將母親的骨灰撒在火雞和布丁上，然後吃下肚子，希望能藉此和母親更加親密，度過一個母女團聚的佳節。<br />\n<br />\n帕森斯（Debra Parsons）將母親的遺體火化之後，先把骨灰裝在自製的木盒中，打算想一個自己的方式來紀念母親，「我不想撒在外面，那像是我把媽媽遺棄了，但只要骨灰還在身邊，我就感覺她沒離開。」<br />\n<br />\n想了好久都沒想到好方式，帕森斯突然無意識地把手指伸入骨灰，沾了一點來嘗味道，沒想到味道還不錯「粉粉的、鹹鹹的，吃起來很舒服，有被安慰的感覺！」從此以後，她也開始每天都用手指或湯匙服用一點母親的骨灰。<br />\n<br />\n「沾骨灰來吃可以讓我感覺媽媽跟我在一起，但是主題是聖誕節的話，我希望媽媽能成為節慶的一部份，沒錯，我要把她（骨灰）用在聖誕大餐！」<br />\n<br />\nsource: <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/i-eat-mum-christmas-day-11706456?ICID=FB_mirror_main\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mirror.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-news%2Fi-eat-mum-christmas-day-11706456%3FICID%3DFB_mirror_main&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=04ffa8eb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mirror.co.uk/news/uk-news/i-eat-mum-christmas-day-11706456?ICID=FB_mirror_main</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171217/1074150.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171217%2F1074150.htm&d=CbnD%2Fe2fgdhdmOHQVZijsXadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=a8ff3d6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171217/1074150.htm</a>"},{"pid":"b46903296fdedbf35056e1633dc0d442abfa6a25","tid":501737,"uid":82917,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-